{"id": 2047, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常生活里，你都被哪些商家的“确认信息”烦到了？", "description": "那些坚持不懈的苦口婆心是怎么把你逼到欲哭无泪的。", "record_count": 12578, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171204165413Vq2ktM4RYvNETdlz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-04T17:00:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 3378, "title": "日常生活里，你都被哪些商家的“确认信息”烦到了？", "content": "日常里，你都被哪些商家的“确认信息”烦到了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 252550, "content": "去便利店买东西，支付完同时收到信用卡、便利店和微信的确认信息", "image": "img/option/option/201712041632232NP9AiVloJCymBtk.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252552, "content": "不想升级，但每次都会弹出升级提醒，反复确认", "image": "img/option/option/20171204163337OGamHowVKlNA7Bj3.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252553, "content": "充了一个月会员，第二天就开始通知，“您的会员只剩28天啦，充值吗”", "image": "img/option/option/20171204163704xFlPEAJ5tzk6X2rf.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252554, "content": "关闭推送，每次打开app都弹出“为了避免错过福利，强烈建议您打开呦”", "image": "img/option/option/20171204163925xfSDKWq8mnBHVAco.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252555, "content": "房产中介总会在租到房后小半年里隔三差五来确认还要不要租房", "image": "img/option/option/20171204164005QqLaAXbJTk03EpVW.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252557, "content": "在淘宝上买了双袜子，就收到“您已经成员尊贵会员”的消息，定期发来新品广告", "image": "img/option/option/20171204164237Bw48yNsV3tkOhLij.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252558, "content": "在商店扫二维码付款，就收到已自动关注商家微信号的信息", "image": "img/option/option/201712041645147WlXhsoa3YByUGpF.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252559, "content": "无确认，办理会员套餐，到期后没收到确认通知就自动续费", "image": "img/option/option/20171204164828yxskgMQoBauhUTZS.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}